'From Squeak3.8alpha of ''17 July 2004'' [latest update: #5987] on 6 November 2004 at 6:37:37 pm'!"Change Set:		FasterDistance-spfaDate:			6 November 2004Author:			Stephane RollandinThe implementation of Point>>dist: is very indirect. This simple rewrite make it faster by almost 20%"!!Point methodsFor: 'point functions' stamp: 'spfa 11/6/2004 16:01'!dist: aPoint 	"Answer the distance between aPoint and the receiver."	| dx dy |	dx _ aPoint x - x.	dy _ aPoint y - y.	^ ((dx * dx) + (dy * dy)) sqrt! !